job.title: RVUNL Recruitment 2021- Apply Online for 1075 vacancies in Rajasthan
job.body:
Total vacancies:1075

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Accounts Officer
  • Personnel Officer
  • Assistant Engineer (Electrical)
  • Assistant Engineer (Mechanical)
  • Assistant Engineer (Civil)
  • Assistant Engineer (Control & Instrumentation/Communication)
  • Assistant Engineer (Information Technology)
  • Assistant Engineer (Fire & Safety)
  • Junior Engineer
  • Junior Chemist
  • Informatics Assistant

Description

Latest Rajasthan Government Jobs for graduates have been published by Rajasthan Rajya Vidyut Utpadan Nigam Limited(RVUNL) for Assistant Engineer and other vacancies in Rajasthan. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Assistant Engineer and others, from 07-06-2021, and till  21-06-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • For UR (Gen)/EWS if the annual income of the family is Rs.2.50 lakh/ more: Rs 1600/-
  • For UR (Gen)/EWS if annual income of of family is less than Rs.2.50 lakh/ SC/ ST/ BC/ MBC/ PWD (PH): Rs. 1400/-

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 07-06-2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is  21-06-2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40  years old. 

Detailed vacancies with educational qualification:


RVUNL Assistant Engineer and other Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Rajasthan Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 56,100/-.

How to apply for RVUNL Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Assistant Engineer and others. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of RVUNL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by RVUNL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
